[F]愛了我，在我[C]愛祢之[F]前。称為   ài liǎo wǒ zài wǒ ài mí zhī qián chēng wéi
firstlovedme：Iongbe-fore-lovedYou.Youhave
[F/A]我死在十[B]架，耶[F/C]穌，耶[C]穌称好愛[F]我。耶   wǒ sǐ zài shí jià yē sū yē sū chēng hǎo ài wǒ yē
diedup-ontheCross.YougaveYourbloodtosetmefree.You
